the to-do list, I have a to-do list in here that's just absurd. I mean, just like none

00:15:49.099 --> 00:15:55.219
of that stuff I'm ever gonna do. So, going back and redoing stuff that I've already done

00:15:55.219 --> 00:16:01.340
just seems like, I mean, it works. I don't have any tests that would prove it. But I

